    "incident_name": "Suppliers vendor-portal sensor hangs indefinitely",
    "category": "Stuck/Hung Job",
    "severity": "Sev-1 (Critical)",
    "description": "Stuck/Hung Job incident on the Suppliers pipeline (RTL_SUP_STUCK): suppliers vendor-portal sensor hangs indefinitely.",
    "symptoms": "ExternalTaskSensor waiting on the vendor portal's 'file ready' flag has been in poke state for 14+ hours with no timeout configured.",
    "root_cause": "The vendor's upload automation silently failed with no error surfaced to the portal, and the sensor was configured with mode='poke', timeout=None, so Airflow keeps a worker slot occupied indefinitely.",
    "business_impact": "Downstream supplier onboarding and PO matching for the day never runs; 40+ purchase orders unmatched, blocking receiving.",
    "resolution": "Kill the stuck task instance, manually trigger the vendor to re-upload; add a bounded timeout (e.g., 4h) with soft_fail=True and an escalation notification."
  },
